174
02:03:56.429 --> 02:03:57.263
<font face="Serif" size="18">Aurelio.</font>

175
02:03:57.471 --> 02:03:59.640
<font face="Serif" size="18">Aurelio Rosas Sanchez, tamam.</font>

176
02:04:04.770 --> 02:04:06.188
<font face="Serif" size="18">Tamam.</font>

177
02:04:13.571 --> 02:04:16.407
